Frontend:
Backend:
    Endpoints:
        ☐ `/Register`: Registers an account 
        ☐ `/NewProduct`: Uploads a new item for sale
        ☐ `/ModifyProduct`: Changes an item listing
        ☐ `/Items`: Returns a paginated list of items
        ☐  `/ItemDetails`: Returns item details
        ☐  `/PurchaseItem`: Purchases item
    Data Stores:
        ☐ DB table storing accounts
        ☐ DB table storing items and their owners
        ☐ DB table showing purchases and the purchaser
        ☐ Blob storage for images linked to items

